| style="text-align:left;" | {{Flagu|Turkey}}
| 1<ref name="Hürriyet Daily News">{{cite news|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/one-turkish-german-among-150-victims-in-germanwings-plane-crash.aspx?pageID=238&nID=80101&NewsCatID=351 |title=One Turkish-German among 150 victims in Germanwings plane crash|newspaper=[[Hürriyet Daily News]]|date=24 March 2015|accessdate=24 March 2015}}</ref>
